    App
    Entry point for JavaFX application.

    Represents comic issue data including name of issue and path to resource URI.

    Reads and stores API keys as configured inside KeyConfig.json file.

    Represents events data including name of event and path to resource URI.
    InputModel
    Sub model interface for methods relating to interacting with the input Marvel API.
    MainPresenter
    MainPresenter class that observes the ModelFacade and MainView object that is passed in through the constructor.

    MainView class observes the main view through being set as a JavaFX Controller class to (Main.fxml)
    MarvelApiHandler
    API handler that handles sending and retrieving requests to the Marvel web API.
    ModelFacade
    Provides methods for clients to make mutable and accessor calls to APIs.
    ModelImpl
    Provides methods for clients to make mutable and accessor calls to APIs.
    ModelImplTest
    Class used as test suite for testing ModelImpl, an implementation of the ModelFacade interface.
    ModelObserver
    Interface for ModelObserver methods to perform actions based on ModelFacade notifications.
    OfflineMarvelModel
    Dummy offline version implementation of InputModel.
    OfflinePastebinModel

    Online version implementation of InputModel.

    ReportService
    Helper class that creates report string from CharacterInfo object
    ResourceUrl
    Represents events data including type and URL for public website resource.
    ResponseHandler
    Handler for handling JSON response body strings from Marvel API request results.
    Series
    Represents series data including name of series and path to resource URI.
    Story
    Represents story data including name of story and path to resource URI.
    Thumbnail
    Represents thumbnail image data including image path and extension.
    UnitTests  
    ViewObserver
    Interface for ViewObserver methods to listen for UI events.
